<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.7">
<l>kaṉaṅkuḻai yāḷporuṭṭāk kaṇaipārinta rakkartaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>iṉaṅkaḻu vēṟṟuvitta veḻiltōḷemi rāmaṉmalai</l>
<l>kaṉaṅkoḻi teḷḷaruvi vantucūḻntakal ñālamellām</l>
<l>iṉaṅkuḻu vāṭumalai yeḻilmāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of our strong armed Rāma who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having spread arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the lady with the gold earring,</l>
<l rend="indent">raised the family of demons on stakes,</l>
<l>that is beautiful Māliruñcōlai where</l>
<l rend="indent">a gathering of multitudes from the whole of the broad earth</l>
<l rend="indent">come to bathe, surrounding the clear waterfalls that cast gold ashore.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
